Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: altify
Version: 3.0
Summary: Uses deep learning to caption img tags within a web page and fills out their alt attribute with the related caption
Home-page: https://github.com/parhamp/altify
Author: Parham Pourdavood
Author-email: ppourdavood@gmail.com
License: Apache-2.0
Download-URL: https://github.com/parhamp/altify/tarball/0.1
Description: Altify automizes the task of inserting alternative text attributes for imgage tags. Altify uses Microsoft Computer Vision API's deep learning algorithms to caption images in an HTML file and returns a new HTML file in which alt attributes are filled out with their corresponding captions.
Keywords: alt,caption,images,deep learning
Platform: UNKNOWN
